main event: A witness observed a red and green lighted object in Lakewood, California, on 5 July 1966.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 14 minutes, The object was reported to have sped off toward the northeast after initially stopping, The witness described the object as emitting red and green lights, The witness estimated the speed of the object to be between 325-375 mph, The object was observed at a distance of approximately 200 feet.
witness description: A male, 14 years old, who lacks experience or knowledge of rockets, missiles, or aircraft.
